        <text>
            <body>
                <p>
                    <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324654" xml:id="d1e151383">Humbertus, Dei gratia
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e151385">Eduensis</placeName>
                        episcopus</persName>, dilecto sibi in Christo fratri <persName key="d1e22167" xml:id="d1e151389">Villelmo abbati <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e151391">Fonteneti</orgName>
                    </persName> totique ejusdem loci conventui salutem et paternam benedictionem.
                    Postulasti, karissime frater, super donum <persName key="d1e22173" xml:id="d1e151394">Richardi de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324443" xml:id="d1e151396">
                            <foreign>Espire</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName> quod ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e151400">Fonteneti</orgName>, cui Deo auctore presides, de terra sua que ad
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e151403">Fanium</placeName>
                    pertinebat coram me se fecisse recognovit et tunc quoque fecit confirmarem et
                    scriptum inde sigillo pontificalis auctoritatis munitum tibi traderem. Annuans
                    igitur juste petitioni tue primum posterorum noticie presentibus litteris trado
                        <persName key="d1e22179" xml:id="d1e151406">Richardum de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324443" xml:id="d1e151408">
                            <foreign>Espire</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName> volentem proficisci in expeditionem <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#317554" xml:id="d1e151413">Iherosolimitanam</placeName> coram me et multis aliis
                    quos subsc<hi rend="background(red)">rebe</hi>mus recognovisse quod ecclesie
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e151419">Fonteneti</orgName> dederat
                    et tunc quoque dedit totam terram suam de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e151422">Fanio</placeName> et que ad <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e151425">Fanium</placeName> pertinebat
                    ubicumque esset, preter autem aliam terram que ex utraque parte
                        <supplied>aque</supplied> que <geogName xml:id="d1e151434">Brana</geogName>
                    vocatur jacet, <num>vii</num> mansi siti in predicta villa <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e151440">Fanii</placeName> et unus apud
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325264" xml:id="d1e151443">Curcellas</placeName>
                    quos nominatim exprimens se dedisse recognovit et <hi rend="background(magenta)">dedit et unum rusticum <persName key="d1e22185" xml:id="d1e151448">Berardum</persName>
                    </hi> nomine cum tota sobole sua. Huic recognitioni et dono quod actum est inter
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e151451">Tullionem</placeName> et
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324470" xml:id="d1e151455">Lucenniacum</placeName>
                    affuerunt mecum <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324672" xml:id="d1e151458">Obertus prior
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281890" xml:id="d1e151460">Sancti
                            Simphoriani</orgName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e22191" xml:id="d1e151463">Johannes de <persName key="d1e30955" xml:id="d1e151465">Hylari canonicus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#324497" xml:id="d1e151468">Sancte
                            Margarite</orgName></persName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e22197" xml:id="d1e151471">Arnodus decanus
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324366" xml:id="d1e151473">Sedeloci</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e22204" xml:id="d1e151476">Guido
                            <addName>Carbonellus</addName> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#322865" xml:id="d1e151481">Flaviniaco</placeName> archipresbiter</persName>,
                        <persName key="d1e22210" xml:id="d1e151485">Haymo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324424" xml:id="d1e151487">Alisia</placeName>
                        miles</persName>, <persName key="d1e22216" xml:id="d1e151492">Bernardus
                            <addName>Longus</addName> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#322865" xml:id="d1e151497">Flaviniaco</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e22222" xml:id="d1e151500">Hugo
                            <addName>Pilosus</addName> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325003" xml:id="d1e151505">Rocha</placeName> tunc prepositus meus</persName>,
                        <persName key="d1e22228" xml:id="d1e151509">Renaldus major <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e151511">Tullionis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e22234" xml:id="d1e151514">Renerius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325000" xml:id="d1e151516">
                            <foreign>Rivel</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e22241" xml:id="d1e151520">Hugo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e151522">Monte Barro</placeName>
                    </persName> et plures alii. Confirmans igitur hoc donum interdico Dei et nostra
                    auctoritate ne quis de hoc dono ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e151525">Fonteneti</orgName> injuriam inferre presumat. Quod si
                    sciens fecerit, excommunico eum donec predicte ecclesie satisfaciat.</p>
            </body>
